Context: Title for the error dialog when Studio fails to launch
Error message is shown when the user doesn't have WebView2 installed. WebView2 is required for Studio to load the login page correctly.
Source: WebView2 installation required to launch Studio. Click here for installation details.
en-us: WebView2 installation required to launch Studio. Click here for installation details.
